data.description: Located in sought-after Providence Country club, this lovely four bedroom home is on a quiet street.  Primary bedroom is on the main level. There is a study off of one bedroom with a closet and bathroom, which could be considered a 5th bedroom. Very open concept with the kitchen being open to the 2 story great room.  2 car garage. Granite throughout.  Includes an office and sun room. Sun room overlooks in-ground pool.
